PGAPack Utilities

convertfortran.pl  -- Simple perl script to convert the fortran examples to 
		      work on "64-bit" machines -- Alpha, Power Challenge, T3D.

upgrade_script.pl  -- Script to _assist_ in the upgrade from version 0.2 to 
		      version 1.0.  Will catch _most_ of the changes.

wordsizes.c        -- C program to show the sizes of various datastructues
                      used by PGAPack.  Useful for configuration.  See
                      wordsizes.c for more information.



